text: Espen Thorsen (born 27 March 1962) is a Norwegian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Norway Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Porsgrunn
